	<section class="section-box shadow">
	<section class="container">
		<div class="row">
			<header class="highlight span12">
				<h2>Welcome to the Seductive Turtle Gaming Community</h2>			   
			</header>		
			<header class="highlight span12">
				<p>
					Unlike most gaming communities, we mostly hang out in our teamspeak server. Teamspeak is a voice chat client, like Ventrillo, or Mumble, but a little bit more powerful. There is a link to their website below, with a download after the link. You are welcome to join us, even if you don't have a microphone, or if you dont want to talk!</p>
				<p>
					<a href="http://www.teamspeak.com/" class="big-btn">Visit TeamSpeak.com</a>
					<a id="join-teamspeak" href="ts3server://ts.st-gc.org/?port=9987" class="big-btn">Join the TeamSpeak</a>
				</p>
				<p>
					If that link doesnt work, connect to "ts.st-gc.org" in your teamspeak client.<br />
					We also have a forum running. Check it out by clicking the link below.
				</p>
				<p>
					<a href="http://forum.st-gc.org/" class="big-btn">Commmunity Forum</a>
				</p>
			</header>		
		</div>   
	</section>
	</section>
{% endblock %}
